  "trivia": [
    "Enchanted Star Strike is the second 'Enchanted' Skylander, while Enchanted Hoot Loop is the first.",
    "In the game, her hooded cape changes from white to turquoise. If her Soul Gem ability, 'Shooting Stars,' is purchased, the rest of her outfit also changes colors.",
    "The pose in her official artwork is similar to Star Strike's non-LightCore art, except with glowing eyes.",
    "She is the first non-Legendary Alt Deco LightCore figure."
